      <h1> Background</h1>
      <p> Lomi came up to the developers mind as a solution for this problem. <br/>
      "Lomi", lemon in the English word, is usually used as a tradition in the Ethiopian culture at a specific holiday named Epiphany or "Timket" celebrated outdoor.</br>
      Dressed up in their finest, men and women join the crowd to celebrate.When a guy likes a girl he saw at that festival, he throws a lomi on her and expresses that he likes her. Then they will celebrate the holiday together and they date if the girl is interested too.</bold><big><br/>
